name: Hallagårdens Djurpark & Café
abstract: Hallagården har varit i familjens ägo sedan 1966 och utvecklas hela tiden med nyheter. På vårt B&B finns 2 rum (tvåbäddsrum och familjerum) och stuga med egen dusch och toa samt trinettkök där man tar sin egen frukost.

name: Perssons Magasin
abstract: Vi startade Perssons Magasin 2013 med konsthantverk och loppis. För varje år har vi utvecklat verksamheten till det vi har idag. Gården är en bergsmansgård med anor från 1700-talet. Boningshuset där B&B finns är från 1876. I Vita stugan, som är från 1700-talet, finns vårt lilla mysiga kafé med hembakat och lättare luncher. Här kan man också bo om man önskar. Övrig verksamhet är i den stora ladugårdsbyggnaden i fyra våningar. På konsthantverksavdelningen har vi samlat hantverk från ca 40 st lokala hantverkare. I matboden säljer vi lokalproducerat mathantverk och även det vi själva tillverkar av det trädgården ger, som sylt, marmelad, saft mm. I vår konstutställningslokal har konstnärer från Sverige och världen utställningar. Det brukar vara tre olika per sommarsäsong. Loppis finns i fem olika lokaler med ett stort utbud av varor. Trädgården anlades nog när boningshuset byggdes, här finns många stora träd kvar från den tiden. Vi flyttade hit 1972 och har utökat trädgården och anpassat den till våra behov. Trädgården är öppen för besökare och vi erbjuder även en skattjakt för barnen, en vandring med lite spänning, olika aktiviteter och upplevelser.

name: Scandic Europa
abstract: HAK restaurant and bar sets the tone for our hotel, with its welcoming hotel bar, social gatherings, art exhibitions and delicious menu. Come and dine or hang out at our bar. Visit our pool, work out in the gym or relax in the sauna before you head out into town. You can also "switch" office and book a meeting in one of our 14 meeting rooms. We'll help you add a delicious coffee break, lunch or perhaps dinner to round it all off.

name: Scandic Winn
abstract: Whether you're travelling with work, your family, a sports team, or group of friends – our rooms are flexible enough to suit your needs. Our cosy Brasserie is a homely place for all our guests. Choose from our large selection of beers and exciting cocktails, taste seasonal specialities from Varmland or enjoy freshly grilled meat from our rotisserie. Take a dip in our jacuzzi, warm up in our sauna, or give your muscles a work out in our gym. We also have meeting rooms for up to 250 people and we offer WiFi to all our guests.

name: Scandic Norrköping Nord
abstract:
Enjoy a good night's sleep in one of our hotel rooms designed in Scandinavian style, with wallpaper inspired by the natural surroundings of Ostergotland. Exercise in our gym, take a dip in our 25 degree pool or relax in our sauna. 

In our lobby bar we serve lighter meals and beverages. Choose from 13 well-equipped meeting rooms for your events and conferences that can accommodate up to 120 people and have WiFi.

name: Scandic Foresta
abstract: Scandic Foresta has been an important meeting place ever since 1910 when Wilhelmina Skogh opened her medieval castle on the cliff. Hold your next meeting or conference in one of our 7 meeting facilities, or plan an event in our unique party venue in the castle turret. In the evening you can enjoy a delicious dinner in our hotel restaurant Bistro Foresta, with great views over the water and Stockholm. Our hotel also has a lobby bar, shop and gym. As our guest you have access to WiFi throughout the hotel.

name: Scandic Malmen
abstract: When the hunger really hits you, you need to visit our Bar- and Bistro where we serve food influenced by tastes and raw ingredients from the entire world. When the live , and is a popular hangout for an after-work get-together. If hunger sets in, head to our restaurant. When the live performers left the stage, the stage is ideal for lectures or seminars. We offer free WiFi and why not take the opportunity to connect with other business guests. It's a real oasis for those who want to get their creativity flowing during the workday. If you need to clear your head later, swing by our gym or borrow a bike and explore the capital.

name: Scandic Helsingborg Nord
abstract: You can eat well-prepared meals here in our Köksbaren restaurant and relax with a drink in our well-stocked hotel bar. Exercise in our gym, take a swim in our pool, or relax in our sauna. We also have 12 flexible meeting and conference facilities with space for up to 150 people. Let us help you put together the best possible meeting.

name: Scandic Örebro Väst
abstract: After exploring the sights of Orebro you can visit our relaxation suite and relax in our sauna, or take a dip in our pool. End your day with a meal in our Köksbaren restaurant and enjoy a drink in our relaxing bar. Hold your meeting or conference in one of our conference rooms with capacity for up to 180 people. As a hotel guest or conference participant, you always have free WiFi.

name: Scandic Östersund Syd
abstract: Our Köksbaren restaurant is open nearly 24 hours a day. Start your day with an appetising organic breakfast buffet and round off with something delicious from our menu, which offers a good choice of classic and seasonal dishes. If you arrive late at night, our 24-hour shop is always open, selling a range of delicious salads and sandwiches, as well as newspapers and of course toothbrushes, if you happen to have left yours behind. Naturally, we have an excellent gym and relaxation suite, where you can come and unwind whenever you feel like it. We offer free parking for our guests, with engine heaters in the winter, as well as access to free, fast WiFi throughout our hotel.

name: Scandic Gamla Stan
abstract: Das Scandic Foresta ist seit 1910 ein wichtiger Tagungsort – in diesem Jahr öffnete Wilhelmina Skogh zum ersten Mal die Tore ihres Schlosses auf dem Felsenvorsprung. Unser Hotel verfügt ebenfalls über Lobby-Bar, Shop und Fitnessraum. Als Hotelgast kommen Sie in den Genuss von kostenfreiem W-LAN. „Das Scandic Foresta wurde von TripAdvisor mit dem Traveler's Choice Award 2013 ausgezeichnet, in der Kategorie: Die besten 25 Hotels in Schweden. “

name: Scandic Gällivare
abstract: Scandic Gällivare offers a relaxation suite with indoor pool, gym, jacuzzi and sauna. Our restaurant serves delicious dinners for all ages, and our Scandic shop is packed with goodies. We customise conference packages to suit your requirements and have conference facilities for up to 50 people, as well as smaller meeting rooms for up to 16 people.

name: Scandic Grand Örebro
abstract:
Enjoy a delicious dinner in our restaurant or sit back in our bar for a meeting, lighter snacks and a refreshing drink. Our breakfast offers something for everyone and is of course organic.
With our 8 meeting facilities for up to 170 people, this is the place for everything from small meetings to conferences, events or banquets. Don’t forget to take a break and re-energise in our gym, or unwind in our relaxation suite with jacuzzi and sauna.

name: Scandic Park
abstract: With the buzz of the big city just around the corner together with the warm, homely atmosphere of our hotel, you get the best of both worlds. We serve food and drinks at the bar. Perfect for an early after-work event and a gathering spot for its Ostermalm neighbours. Those who feel like escaping the four walls of the office can hold a smaller conference in our Boardroom overlooking Humlegarden park. When it’s time for bed, one of our spacious rooms will ensure that your family enjoys their stay here too.

name: Scandic Klarälven
abstract: Sleep well in one of our hotel rooms and enjoy our large organic breakfast buffet. Our hotel has a beautiful view over Klaralven river with the town centre as its backdrop, and you can enjoy these views from our newly renovated Köksbaren restaurant with its large outdoor terrace. Swim in our indoor pool, relax in our sauna or exercise on our rowing machine. Our hotel has large, private parking and is located only a 10-minute walk from the city's shopping streets. Our hotel has 6 conference rooms and free WiFi throughout the hotel.

name: Scandic Billingen
abstract: Keep fit in our hotel gym, unwind in our sauna and enjoy delicious dining in our comfortable hotel restaurant. Why not borrow a bicycle from reception and ride around Billingen mountain? At hotel Scandic Billingen, we offer 9 meeting rooms for 2–500 people in beautiful facilities. We offer WiFi to all guests at our hotel.

name: Scandic Klara
abstract: Klara Eat & Meet serves warm food from our a la carte menu and our restaurant is an ideal peaceful setting if you'd like to host a larger breakfast meeting. Stortorget in our courtyard offers our hotel guests a breakfast buffet everyday. Our courtyard is suitable for dinner events and can be rented as well.

name: Scandic Upplands Väsby
abstract: Enjoy food and beverage in our Köksbaren restaurant. Work out in our hotel's well-equipped gym, or unwind in our relaxation suite with jacuzzi and sauna. We have meeting rooms for 2–200 people and we offer WiFi in all our communal areas and hotel rooms at no extra cost.

name: Scandic Go, Upplandsgatan 4
abstract:
We know you want to be free to do your thing, to travel without a headache. To have a safe, comfy place to crash. A quick, savory something when your tummy rumbles. Smart solutions that enable you to focus on more fun things. For all tomorrow’s adventures, spontaneous or planned to a tee, there’s now Scandic Go. Created to offer you the essentials, the bone structure of your trip - a hotel that gives you all the stuff you need and nothing more, with no hidden costs. Welcome to explore a hassle-free hotel stay - this is traveling made easy, by Scandic Go. 

Eat in or take out, but don’t go hungry. No matter the hour, we’ll hook you up with tasty street-style food from the all-day-all-night menu. Hot and cold meals, breakfast, snacks, drinks, you name it. Night owls and early birds, rest assure – there’s always a savory something to be had at Scandic Go.

name: Scandic Linköping City
abstract: At our restaurant Verandan you'll feel the warm and cozy atmosphere. We offer meals from a simple menu in the evenings. In the morning you can look forward to a tasty breakfast buffet. You can enjoy free access to our gym and WiFi. We have 10 conference venues for up to 90 people.

name: Scandic Kramer
abstract: Hotel Scandic Kramer is conducted in a beautiful building from 1878. The hotel is renovated in a way that preserves the 1800s charm. Entering the hotel you're greeted by a stunning staircase with original decorated glass windows. You can enjoy our tasty breakfast buffet in the morning. Work out in our hotel gym and and relax in the sauna during your stay. We also offer conferences for up to 48 participants, and free Wi-Fi at the hotel.

name: Scandic S:t Jörgen
abstract: After a full day of experiences, you can regain new strength in the sauna or clear your head with the help of our gym equipment. If you'd rather prefer to watch sporting events instead, sit back in our lobby and watch some TV. Maybe order a tasty bite from our food bar. In the morning we will serve you our popular breakfast buffet.

name: Scandic Laholmen
abstract: Our hotel has a lounge/lobby bar serving delicious drinks and snacks. Every Friday and Saturday we have live music in our piano bar. Our restaurant serves excellent food from the west coast of Sweden and Oxygen Lounge & Nightclub offers music and dancing on Fridays and Saturdays. We have several meeting rooms, most with harbour views. We also offer a gym, sauna and outdoor parking for your convenience.

name: Scandic Plaza Umeå
abstract: The bright and open spaces in our hotel are suitable for both meetings and relaxation. Unwind in our relaxation suite on the top floor with stunning city and river views. Put your muscles to work in our gym and warm up in our sauna. Enjoy breakfast, lunch and dinner in our excellent restaurant on the ground floor. Our banqueting room is suitable for larger events of up to 170 seated dinner guests.

name: Scandic Örebro Central
abstract:
With us, you'll feel at home despite being away, and in motion despite resting happily in an armchair made of the softest Tarnsjo leather in the calm of the hotel's lush lobby. Flip up your laptop and continue working, or just relax for a moment in your hotel room.

The hotel has a personal touch and invites you to meet friends old and new, from all over the country. The lobby is designed as a living room, divided by green curtains of vegetation and dotted with soft armchairs and comfortable seats that invite you either to work or wind down.

Here you can relax with a bite to eat, quench your thirst or hold a digital meeting. The warm, open lobby combines sustainable materials with timeless values and innovative design solutions. The interior boasts wood, leather and stone, which are not only beautiful, durable natural materials that age with dignity, but also provide a connection with Orebro’s proud tradition of craftsmanship.

name: Scandic Arvika
abstract: Scandic Arvika is a cosy hotel set within one of the oldest houses in Arvika from the 19th century, where charm and sentiments still linger in the walls. Our hotel offers a tranquil relaxation suite with pool, whirlpool, wet sauna, steam sauna and gym. Our hotel guests enjoy free access to our relaxation suite. We have meeting and conference facilities at Scandic Arvika which are also ideal for dinners and exhibitions. In our Stefan på Statt restaurant we serve excellent food with varying themes according to the season. In the summer, we open our outdoor terrace and bar.

name: Scandic No 25
abstract: The atmosphere here is relaxed. Our hotel rooms are decorated in pale Scandinavian colors and on the top floor of the hotel, we have 2 unique meeting facilities for up to 40 or 20 people, which are suitable for both meetings and social occasions. We also offer parking in a secure garage; however pre-booking is not possible. We serve breakfast in the morning and during the evenings our food bar is open.

name: Scandic Elmia
abstract: Scandic Elmia har fået et ansigtsløft. Slap af i vores sauna, hold formen i vores fitnessrum, eller kig forbi fritidscenteret Rosenlundsbadet, som ligger lige ved siden af vores hotel med vandland og spa. Til cyklister har vi også et opbevaringsrum til cykler samt det vigtigste værktøj. Nogle værelser har desuden vægmonterede cykelstativer. Vi kan også hjælpe dig med at arrangere vellykkede møder eller konferencer. Vores 13 moderne mødefaciliteter har plads til op til 100 personer, og vi tilbyder fri WiFi og fri parkering. Føl dig hjemme i vores restaurant Köksbaren, hvor vi serverer mad med en kvalitet, der er sjælden at finde på vejrestauranter, inklusive vores lækre Scandic Klassikere. Vi vil have at du føler dig hjemme, så slap af foran den åbne pejs, eller du kan udfordre nogen til et spil pool.

name: Scandic Frimurarehotellet
abstract: Venture away from our hotel to explore the attractions in Linkoping. Just a block from Scandic Frimurarehotellet are the city's shopping streets and beautiful cathedral. Gamla Linkoping and the Swedish Air Force Museum are both popular excursions within easy reach of our hotel. Go for a walk along the Stangan river or jog through Rydskogen forest. Our hotel is located close to the railway station and just 3 km from Linkoping Airport.

name: Scandic Stortorget
abstract: You’ll find us in a turn-of-the-century building on Stortorget. History blends with beautiful decor here: an ideal place for both meetings and relaxation. After a day of shopping, a chance to unwind in our gym may be just what you need. Or how about relaxing in our lobby bar for a while before the evening’s activities? If you’re holding a meeting, we’ll be happy to help. We have conference and meeting rooms for up to 70 people. If your group is bigger than that, we work in partnership with Frimurarlogen in Malmo, which has a wonderful banqueting and event room for up to 200 people.

name: Scandic Sundsvall Nord
abstract: Getting here by car is easy and convenient. We have 150 free parking spaces, 90 of which have engine heaters. Have a bite to eat in our newly renovated Köksbaren restaurant before getting some rest in our comfortable beds. Have a warming sauna, cool down in our pool, or work out in our gym. We have conference opportunities here for both large and small meetings, with our largest room able to accommodate 160 people. All our conference venues are equipped with modern technology and free WiFi.

name: Scandic Continental
abstract: Relax with your favorite mixed drink in the bar on our roof terrace. Work out in our gym or relax in our sauna. At Scandic Continental we offer meeting rooms for up to 900 participants.

name: Scandic Kungens Kurva
abstract: Unwind in our sauna, take a dip in our indoor pool, exercise in our gym. We offer free WiFi to all our guests.

name: Scandic Gävle Väst
abstract: After a delicious dinner in our restaurant, head to our bar and enjoy a relaxing drink. Give your muscles a work out in our modern gym, take a dip in our pool and unwind in our sauna. We have 11 meeting rooms for conferences and events, for up to 250 people. Free WiFi is available throughout our hotel. Head to reception and borrow a bike to explore the area around our hotel. Our free parking is much appreciated by our guests.

name: Scandic Grand Central
abstract:
If you could put a stethoscope on Stockholm, its heartbeat would probably be loudest just where Scandic Grand Central is located – the hotel that seems to have always been there. The historic building, formerly known as the Lundberg Palace, was constructed by builder C.O. Lundberg in 1885. The Vasa Theatre is also here and, after a few years’ break, is back raising its red curtain once again. This magnificent stage for grand events, shows and concerts with seating for 800 people became a reality once more when the theatre was coupled with Scandic Grand Central in September 2016. Immerse yourself in the history of the period features. Huge illuminated windows invite you in to participate. 
With space for 800 standing guests (470 seated), Vasa Theatre is also perfect for all types of event. Our hotel offers flexible meeting and conference rooms for up to 380 participants. 

Urban scenery awaits you at Scandic Grand Central, created by the remarkable combination of bars and restaurants. Shape your very own unique experience with live music, art and DJs all at your fingertips. There is never a dull moment! Welcome to Scandic Grand Central with 391 rooms. A modern classic that has stood the test of time.

name: Scandic Landvetter
abstract:
You'll be sure to have a good night's sleep in our rooms set in calm Nordic colors. Our comfy beds help you to relax and recharge your batteries to take on new challenges or wind down after a hectic day. No need to stress in the morning, the gate is located with only a few minutes' walk from your hotel door.

Regardless if you have hours or days to spend before boarding, you’ll be excited when visiting our restaurant. The interior makes your mind wander to our Nordic environment. Be tempted by the variation in beers, drinks and a mix of urban dishes, altogether you can relax and enjoy modern and fresh comfort food influenced by Sweden. Depending on how much time you have on your hand, you can tailor make your menu. Try a tasty dinner with your loved ones, or an energy boosted breakfast before your long distance flight.

Besides meeting new and old travel companions, the locals "Gothenburgers" as well as long distance travelers will check in to create memories, discuss and make important decisions. The new and modern meeting area is available around the clock, and is created for late evenings as well as efficient meetings for early birds before boarding. Different time zones are no problems thanks to the use of hybrid meetings and depending on guests and atmosphere you can imagine yourself to be either in London or New York as in Gothenburg.

No matter if you just got home, make a stopover or is just about to start your journey, a visit to our relaxation area will not let you down. Lean back in the hot tub or get warmed up in the sauna and watch people from all over starting their journey from the runway.

name: Scandic Göteborg Central
abstract:
Batten down the hatches, all hands on deck! A new hotel has anchored in the Port of Gothenburg. Its sheer size gives it a powerful presence even at a distance, and once you’re inside you can’t help but be seduced by the atmosphere; it’s as if the pulse from the city has found its way through the entrance doors with you. Relax in the comfortable sofas, sit down with your laptop at the large worktables, or quench your thirst in the lobby bar — this hotel will fit your every need. 

At Scandic Göteborg Central, you’ll always have a good night's sleep in one of our 451 rooms, which are decorated in calm, Nordic colors. The rooms have large glass windows and smart detailing. In our comfortable beds, you can unwind after a busy workday or gather energy for a day on the town. Your breakfast is served in an exciting environment with inspiration from different continents. 

The food bar and bar are close to the reception and together they create a boundless living room. A place to hang out at all hours of the day, alone and together. On the terrace on the fourteenth floor, Gothenburg opens up with a fantastic view of the river, the Old Town, and the harbor.

The hotel has very generous and flexible meeting and conference facilities. The largest meeting room, with six meters to the ceiling, can host up to 1000 standing or 900 seated participants. There are another 18 meeting rooms for versatile use.

name: Scandic Oceanhamnen
abstract:
Feel right at home at Scandic Oceanhamnen, in one of our 184 rooms decorated in calm, Nordic colours inspired by the sea. Our hotel enjoys a front row seat by the sea, in an urban archipelago with fantastic pedestrian walkways along the pier. You step right from the quay into our personal and welcoming hotel. You’ll find everything you need here from early morning until late night. 

In addition to sustainable food and beverage, our kitchen, bar and restaurant offer several different co-working spaces as well as comfortable sofas and armchairs for spontaneous meetings. The location of our open-air café right by the sea is hard to beat. Enjoy the sound of the lapping waves as you gaze out over the sound towards Denmark. 

Our relaxation suite offers breathtaking panoramic views. The glittering coast lies at your feet here. Relax among green plants in the hanging armchairs, practice some yoga in the morning sun, or enjoy a sauna at dusk. 

Our hotel offers exclusive and flexible meeting opportunities. At the top of the building on the roof terrace is Studio Oceanhamnen, an outstanding meeting room with unbeatable sea views and a generous terrace. Another 3 meeting rooms are located on the ground floor, the largest of which can accommodate 70 seated guests.

Our rooms are located on floor 1-4 and floor 12.

Welcome to Scandic Oceanhamnen, your sustainable living room by the sea.

name: Scandic Crown
abstract: Enjoy a delicious breakfast at our Brasserie Crown and in the evening we serve our à la carte menu, and after dinner you can relax in one of our comfortable armchairs in our bar. If you think you’ve had too much of a good thing, jump on the treadmill in our gym, unwind in our sauna or slip into our jacuzzi and enjoy the breathtaking views from our relaxation suite.

name: Scandic No. 53
abstract:
Our hotel rooms are modern and packed with smart solutions such as a dimmer and rain shower in the private bathroom, as well as plenty of mirrors. Enjoy a good night's sleep in the comfortable bed, big enough for two. Hang your clothes on the practical knobs and hangers. Our standard plus rooms are equipped with a desk. Otherwise, why not try working in our comfortable, large lounge which, with its Community tables, is ideal for new, inspirational meetings. 

We serve breakfast buffet in the morning and in the evenings you can order pinsa and something sweet from our food bar. Work in comfort with your own plug socket for your computer plus plenty of space for smaller meetings or an after-work event. Free WiFi is available throughout our hotel. Our charming courtyard is a magnet for both Stockholm locals and hotel guests during the summer months. Parking is available close by at Norra Latin and in Stockholm City Garages.

name: Scandic Victoria Tower
abstract: The architect firm Wingårdh is responsible for this fantastic building, which is completely covered in glass. Our entire hotel features designer furniture from Vitra, Montana and Flos. Our lobby, lounge and restaurant flow into each other, creating a social arena suitable for working, meeting, eating, drinking and relaxing. Our hotel  has 15 conference rooms, spread over the lobby floor and 33rd floor with its heavenly view. Last but not least, our gym and sauna are on the 22nd floor – with the same wonderful view, of course.

name: Scandic Umeå Syd
abstract: At hotel Scandic Umeå Syd we have a gym which is open 24 hours a day for all our hotel guests. When you stay with us, you can swim in our pool and relax in our sauna. In the evening you can enjoy a dinner in our hotel restaurant. Our bar serves hot and cold drinks in front of an open fire. Hold meetings and conferences at our hotel and WiFi is always free.

name: Scandic Växjö
abstract: You can take a dip in our pool, visit our sauna or fit in a workout at the gym. Enjoy an excellent meal in our restaurant or get down to business in one of our 3 meeting rooms that can accommodate from 2 to 55 people. Småland airport is only 7 minutes away by car.

name: Scandic Visby
abstract: Vårt nye hotell i Visby har 214 rom, mange med havutsikt og balkong eller terrasse. Komplekset omfatter også konferansefasiliteter, to restauranter, svømmebasseng, utendørs spa og et treningsrom.

name: Scandic Hallandia
abstract: When you stay with us at Scandic Hallandia you can unwind in our relaxation suite with sauna, jacuzzi and fantastic views of Halmstad. Our hotel restaurant, SVEA, offers dinner, as well as cocktails in its charming bar. You can host a meeting for up to 100 people in our conference facilities. Take the opportunity to borrow a bike from reception and explore Halmstad.

name: Scandic Kalmar Väst
abstract: Take a dip in our indoor pool at hotel Scandic Kalmar Väst and then relax in our sauna. Enjoy good food in our Calmare Nyckel restaurant. Our hotel has 6 meeting rooms for 2–80 people and we offer internet access in all the communal areas.

name: Scandic Karlstad City
abstract: Here at Scandic Karlstad City you can sit back in our inviting lounge and enjoy a moment’s relaxation, or why not meet up with some friends and enjoy dinner or something lighter in our restaurant. Give your mind a rest in our relaxation suite. Here you find the sauna, jacuzzi and gym. Round off your evening with a coffee, or a drink in our bar. Our restaurant with its adjoining lounge has a relaxed atmosphere, which is ideal for a small get together of 2 to 3 people.

name: Scandic Södertälje
abstract: We offer a well-equipped gym with pool and sauna. Play a game or two of table football or have a drink in our bar, before enjoying a delicious dinner buffet in our hotel restaurant Koksbaren. Borrow a bicycle from reception and explore some of the older parts of Sodertalje. Our hotel offers 5 recently renovated meeting rooms, equipped with the latest technology. We also offer free WiFi to all our guests.

name: Scandic Västerås
abstract: Scandic Västerås has a relaxation suite with indoor pool, sauna and gym. Enjoy a meal in Köksbaren restaurant, open a few days a week, or a drink in our bar. Our hotel also has 7 meeting rooms with free WiFi.

name: Haymarket by Scandic
abstract:
Our restaurants are in a class of their own, with something for foodies and party-goers, lunch guests, coffee-loving window-shoppers, 'out of office' entrepreneurs, and demanding event organisers. Our flexible event room hosts everything from fashion shows, film premiers and massive New Year festivities, The interior is easily adapted from meeting room to large open space to create unique events and social gatherings. We also have a small cinema with dark red velvet armchairs for meetings with a different setting.

Original features of the building where Greta Garbo worked in the 1920s have been carefully preserved, restored or reinterpreted for the coming 2020s. The magical and cinematic feel is a stark contrast to the modern and cosmopolitan features, creating an extraordinary design experience.

name: Scandic Backadal
abstract: If you don't want to rest in bed, you can always unwind in front of our open fire or challenge the family to a game of darts, table football or table tennis. We are well prepared for your conference at our hotel. After a long day of activities you may need to unwind, and our relaxation suite will be waiting for you. We have a pool, sauna and gym.

name: Scandic Mölndal
abstract: This is a great place to stay, just far enough away from the stress and noise of the city. If you’ve had a long day, why not relieve tension in our gym or let your thoughts gently drift away in a hot sauna or jacuzzi. With our guest parking and convenient public transport to Liseberg and the Swedish Exhibition Centre, we provide a fantastic base from which to enjoy a family holiday or business trip. We arrange effective conferences of all sizes. In the morning you can look forward to our tasty breakfast buffet.

name: Scandic Luleå
abstract: Visit our relaxation suite at Scandic Luleå and take a dip in our indoor pool or relax in our sauna. We have bicycles you can borrow if you wish to explore Lulea yourself. Enjoy Swedish dishes and specialities from the Norrbotten region, such as reindeer and elk, in our hotel restaurant. Our hotel has conference rooms for up to 100 people and we offer free WiFi to all our guests.

name: Scandic Sundsvall City
abstract:
Look forward to our tasty breakfast buffet in the morning. You can buy salads, sandwiches and other goodies from our shop in the lobby. 

As our guest you enjoy free access to our sauna, gym and relaxation suite. Free WiFi is available throughout our hotel. Hold your conference in one of our 6 meeting rooms. Our largest meeting facilities can accommodate 40 people. Plenty of public parking is available nearby on the streets and the square.

name: Scandic Segevång
abstract: We offer our guests a variety of activities when they stay with us. Dining in our Köksbaren restaurant, relaxation by the open fire in our lobby, and a refreshing dip in our indoor pool, to name but a few. All guests also have WiFi access from anywhere in the hotel.

name: Scandic Norra Bantorget
abstract: You can choose between many different room types, and several of our rooms have views over the rooftops of Stockholm. The whole family can stay in one of our family rooms – the largest ones can accommodate 5 people and guests of all ages will appreciate the view. Kids usually like to point out all the fun things they can see from so high up. If you're travelling alone, you can get a peaceful night's sleep in one of our extra quiet cabins, with windows facing the corridor. In the summertime you can enjoy our breakfast buffet on our outdoor terrace.

name: Scandic Linköping Väst
abstract: Enjoy an à la carte dinner in our Köksbaren restaurant. Exercise in our gym or take a dip in our pool. If you prefer outdoor exercise, you can borrow one of our bikes from reception. Hold your next meeting or conference in one of our meeting rooms with free WiFi.

name: Scandic Strömmen
abstract:
In 2019, a brand new building was added to Scandic Strömmen, formerly Scandic Norrköping City, with 74 new hotel rooms, a new restaurant, a roof terrace mini pool and an indoor mini pool.  

Enjoy a wonderful breakfast in the morning. Restaurant Tegel offers a simple à la carte menu and during the high season kids get to choose from their very own kids’ menu. Free WiFi is available throughout the hotel and rooms. Relax with a dip in one of our mini pools, work out in our gym, or enjoy a warming sauna. Or borrow one of our bikes if you prefer outdoor exercise.

name: Scandic Anglais
abstract:
Choose from our 2 bars if you want something to drink, one of which is said to have the longest bar counter in Stockholm. Bar Anglais is just as suitable for lively after-work drinks with music and classic bar meals as it is for informal meetings with laptops. Enjoy the view over the rooftops and the National Library from our wonderful roof terrace in the summer months.

Stay in shape at our well-equipped gym, or relax in the sauna. We also have bikes which you can borrow. Perfect if you want to combine sightseeing with a little exercise. You can also book meeting rooms for 2–200 people, and we can arrange events for up to 500 guests.

name: Scandic Swania
abstract: When you stay with us at Scandic Swania, you can take a dip in our indoor pool, keep fit at our gym and relax in our sauna. Hold meetings and conferences in one of our conference facilities for up to 170 people; we can also arrange banquets for up to 400 people. We offer free WiFi to all guests at our hotel.

name: Scandic Arlandastad
abstract:
Enjoy a comfortable stay near your gate in one of our 150 rooms furnished in Scandinavian style with light woods and subtle textiles, which create a harmonious and cosy feeling. Our restaurant offers delicious dining in a relaxed atmosphere. Exercise at our well-equipped gym or relax in our sauna. Modern meeting facilities of various sizes available for up to 100 participants.

When you stay with us, we have parking solutions to offer. Book your transfer to and from the airport, read more on the Parking page. If you are catching a flight, you can park in the long-term car park next to the hotel. Free WiFi is included in all communal areas and all rooms.

name: Scandic Skellefteå
abstract:
When you stay with us, you can relax in our relaxation suite with its pool and gym, or enjoy a delicious dinner in our hotel restaurant. For us, the taste experience is very important. Our inspiring menu offers food from all corners of the world along with a touch of Norrland.

Treat yourself to a well-shaken cocktail or a hot cup of coffee in our hotel bar and lounge, or just sit back, relax and feel right at home in the warm, open surroundings.

name: Scandic Infra City
abstract: Unser Hotel ist der ideale Austragungsort für kleine als auch große Konferenzen. Wir haben eine eigene Ausstellungshalle, einen Bankettsaal und einen Kongresssaal mit Platz für bis zu 1.800 Personen. Wenn Sie nach etwas Spektakulärem suchen, empfehlen wir Ihnen unsere 650 m² große Penthouse Suite mit eigenem Tagungsraum für 50 Teilnehmer.

name: Scandic Skärholmen
abstract: We offer 208 comfortable rooms and contemporary conference facilities, the largest of which has capacity for up to 120 people. Our lobby is connected to our restaurant and is an open meeting place with activities such as billiards and shuffleboard. We also offer free parking, a 24-hour gym, private relaxation suite with sauna, and many other facilities to ensure your comfort and relaxation during your stay.

name: Scandic Värnamo
abstract:
Scandic Värnamo is ideal for both summer holidaymakers and business travellers. 
Take care of business in our 7 flexible meeting rooms, all with free WiFi. In our Prosecco bar you can enjoy both small and larger meals with Italian flavours and unwind with a delicious drink in our bar. Exercise in our gym and relax in our sauna. You can also borrow a bike free of charge from our hotel and explore the city yourself. Apladalen open-air museum and park and the Bruno Mathsson Centre (design museum) are both within a 10-minute walk of our hotel. Isaberg mountain resort is 35 minutes by car and Ullared is 91 km away.

name: Scandic Plaza Borås
abstract: At Scandic Plaza we offer spacious hotel rooms with extra comfort and flexible meeting and conference facilities for up to 130 participants. Our respected relaxation suite is located at the top of the Plaza tower with a gym, sauna and jacuzzi. Enjoy dinner in our comfortable hotel restaurant. After dinner, drop by our bar and enjoy a moment's relaxation. As our guest you have access to WiFi throughout the hotel.

name: Scandic Portalen
abstract:
After a day packed with shopping and adventure, you can relax in our sky sauna with views of Jonkoping. If you would rather get some exercise, Nordic Wellness Atlantis SPA is next door, with direct access from our hotel.

Enjoy a lighter meal and drinks in our lobby bar. WiFi is available throughout our hotel and if you'd like to explore the city yourself, why not borrow a bike from reception. We are also close to golf courses, as well as ski slopes for the winter months.

name: Downtown Camper by Scandic
abstract:
Welcome to our inspirational lifestyle hotel with an atmosphere that promotes affinity, creativity, curiosity and the joy of discovery. As a hotel guest, you can enjoy our daily activities at no extra cost, ranging from yoga to expeditions and inspirational lectures. At Downtown Camper, nature meets metropolis, and Stockholm locals meet visitors. Here, luxury means generosity, togetherness, inspiration and experiences. Perhaps this is why the White Guide ranks our hotel as one of Sweden’s best hotels in 2019, winning the category 'This year’s ‘Forward’ – the most innovative hotel 2019'. 

Our 494 rooms range from small smart rooms to suites with magnificent views over Stockholm. Travelling with friends and family? Book connecting rooms with communal social areas where you can hang out together just like at home but with room service! For up to 12 people. Rather than traditional conference rooms, we've opted for 18 creative spaces of varying sizes, each with a character of its own.

name: Scandic Kiruna
abstract:
At Scandic Kiruna you'll have a good night's sleep after a long day of exploring. Our 231 rooms are decorated in calm, Nordic colors such as beige and warm rust red tones. The rooms have large glass windows and smart details, suitable for both long and short stays. In our comfortable beds you can relax and fill up on energy for next day's meetings or for new adventures in the great outdoors.

The interior design is inspired by the surrounding nature and seasons and with details from the hiking and climbing world. Have a seat in the lobby bar for a few hours of work or enjoy a cup of coffee by the campfire. Maybe the hikers next to you will tell you some breathtaking stories from today's adventures, or you'll start chatting with the group of miners at the bar celebrating the end of their shift.

The restaurant is located on the entrance floor. It's reminiscent of a modern climbers basecamp and offers delicious and well-cooked food based on local ingredients. Sustainability is a theme throughout the building and applies to food and beverage as well. From the base camp, the hike continues up to the top, to Kiruna's one and only, magnificent sky bar. Take the stairs or the elevator and be greeted by the view over the Swedish mountains. Lean back and admire the beautiful nature, the modern city, and with a little bit of luck you can catch the magical northern lights. 

The hotel has flexible conference facilities with seven meeting rooms that can accommodate between fifteen and 300 people. Of course, the rooms can be adapted as needed. The largest conference room is on the entrance floor and the remaining five are located on the first floor from where a skywalk is leading directly to the congress hall in Kulturhuset.

name: Scandic CH
abstract: At Scandic CH you can relax in our sauna or keep fit at our modern gym. Our hotel restaurant offers a tasty breakfast buffet in the morning and food from our food bar in the evening. We can help you arrange conferences and we offer WiFi throughout our hotel to all our guests.

name: Scandic Karlskrona
abstract: The design of our hotel is inspired by our proximity to the Baltic Sea, and natural materials have been used widely. Our restaurant has views over the water, and you can eat out on our large terrace in the summer. Enjoy a good night's sleep, exercise in our gym, or borrow a pair of walking poles to discover Karlskrona on foot. Well-equipped meeting rooms are available for meetings and events and free WiFi is available throughout our hotel. If you arrive by boat, we have 5 moorings right next to our hotel that our guests can use free of charge.

name: Scandic Star Lund
abstract: We are one of southern Sweden’s premier meeting facilities, with conference opportunities for over 400 people in our own theatre and seating for 450 dinner guests in our banqueting suite. Through smart solutions for everything from conferences to TV recordings and concerts, we open up a realm of possibilities. With no event too big or too small, our venues are suitable for every conceivable event. Experience flavors in our relaxed hotel restaurant. Work up an appetite by going for a walk or a jog in the surrounding area. Then unwind in our pool, warm up in our sauna or give your muscles a workout in our gym.

name: Scandic Kista
abstract: Our hotel has 149 rooms, all adapted to cater to the specific requirements of our guests. If you plan to book a longer stay with us, we offer a room type that has access to a fully equipped kitchen. Our lobby is connected to our bar and is a fun meeting place with activities such as billiards and shuffleboard. We also offer conference rooms, a laundry room, parking, 24-hour gym, relaxation suite with sauna, and many other facilities to ensure your comfort during your stay. Relax in our restaurant, bar, or on our outdoor terrace with something delicious to eat or drink.

name: Scandic Täby
abstract: Hold a meeting in one of our hotel's meeting rooms for up to 80 people, all with free WiFi. Exercise at our gym or relax in our sauna. Our hotel also has Köksbaren, a great bar and restaurant.

name: Scandic Talk
abstract: We offer meeting facilities for up to 200 people and our hotel is located right next to Stockholmsmässan. If you arrive by car we offer parking in the garage below the hotel subject to availability and to a cost. If you'd like to use the sauna or work out you're welcome to visit our gym.

name: Scandic Rubinen
abstract:
Scandic Rubinen is a hotel where design and details are in focus and holds the best location on the Avenyn. Stay right in the center of the action. Our 292 hotel rooms range from smaller cozy rooms to suites with magnificent views of Gothenburg. Stay fit in our well-equipped gym or relax in the sauna. Perfect location for your sightseeing tour.

Restaurant Ruby is a meeting point for both locals and hotel guests with its bistro atmosphere, greenery, industrial details and timeless materials. The kitchen offer a menu with a Nordic touch. Between April and October our open air restaurant is open facing Avenyn. 

During the summer, you can enjoy refreshing drinks and a stunning view over the rooftops from our Rooftop bar on the 7th floor. 

We have a floor with its own terrace dedicated entirely to events for meetings and events with up to 180 people. Up here you have your own private boule court.

Our relaxation suite has a sauna where you can unwind, or if you prefer, you can work out in our gym.

name: Scandic Triangeln
abstract:
Scandic Triangeln has 20 floors with large, bright rooms offering a fantastic view of Malmo. Our 18 recently renovated meeting rooms are each slightly different in nature and functionality, which means we have the perfect room for your specific conference. Book our flexible meeting facilities for conferences and customise for an event or party for up to 450 people. Whether you're planning a celebratory dinner, networking event or trade fair, our spectacular Ballroom and large, open spaces are ideal. 

Both residents of Malmo and hotel guests meet for delicious food and beverage at our restaurant. When you stay with us you can also keep fit in our hotel gym, unwind in our sauna, or treat yourself to a spa treatment.

name: Scandic Stora Hotellet
abstract: Enjoy delicious food in our Voyage restaurant, or try some Scotch whisky at our malt whisky bar. Relax in our hotel jacuzzi or exercise in our gym. Here at Scandic Stora Hotellet, we can arrange meetings and conferences for up to 200 participants. Free WiFi is available throughout our hotel.

name: Scandic Lugnet Falun
abstract: Enjoy good food, delicious drinks or a cup of coffee in our cosy restaurant with open fire. Our comfortable rooms are just as suitable for business trips as they are for trips with the family or football team. Relax in our hotel pool, sauna or gym. And you can of course enjoy free WiFi throughout our hotel. Our meeting facilities are suitable for events of up to 60 people.

name: Scandic Malmö City
abstract: Our large hotel rooms and smart kitchen solutions make Scandic Malmö City unique. Our rooms are just as suitable for a family holiday as for business travellers looking for a bit more space. The hotel is located right in the heart of central Malmo.

name: Scandic Skogshöjd
abstract: Grab something light to eat from our bar menu, or choose your favorite drink. Treat yourself to a relaxing time in our first-class hotel relax, which includes a pool and jacuzzi.

name: Scandic Järva Krog
abstract: Enjoy delicious dishes in our cosy restaurant and order your favourite drink at our bar. Exercise in our gym and unwind in our relaxation suite which offers a whirlpool and sauna. Our hotel's beautiful surroundings may well tempt you to go for a jog, walk, or, in summer, even have a picnic. We have meeting and event rooms for up to 110 people and free WiFi is available throughout our hotel.

name: Scandic Uplandia
abstract: When you stay with us at Scandic Uplandia, you can relax and enjoy a tasty breakfast in the morning and something simple in the evening. All our hotel guests have free access to our relaxation suite with sauna and gym. Are you planning to hold a meeting, conference or event? We can provide flexible meeting and conference venues for up to 130 delegates in a bright and airy environment.

name: Scandic Bollnäs
abstract: Enjoy good, organic food in our cosy restaurant. You can work out in our gym and unwind in our sauna. For conferences, we also have 12 meeting rooms which can accommodate 2-200 people. WiFi is of course available throughout our hotel.

name: Scandic Alvik
abstract: You can host a meeting, conference or party for up to 360 people in our conference facilities with plenty of natural light. We always serve a breakfast buffet to give you strength for the day ahead. In addition, we have excellent workout opportunities with a smaller gym at our hotel and a large SATS gym in the building next door. Jogging trails along Alvik Strand are on our doorstep.

name: Scandic Star Sollentuna
abstract: Here at Scandic Star Sollentuna, we have the capacity for 450 guests to dine, hold conferences and sleep under the same roof, making our hotel the perfect place for large meetings and conventions. In our gym at Scandic Star Sollentuna, we have a pool and sauna plus our own spa area, Star Spa.

name: Scandic Uppsala Nord
abstract: We have a relaxation suite with gym and sauna. You can play play billiards in our bar after a delicious dinner in our Köksbaren hotel restaurant. We offer parking outside our hotel at no extra cost. We also offer 13 bright meeting facilities for up to 190 people, as well as free WiFi.

name: Scandic Borlänge
abstract: In the morning we serve our breakfast buffet, and in the evenings you are welcome to enjoy dinner in our restaurant. Unwind in our indoor pool with sauna or work your muscles in our gym. Visit our cosy lobby bar with comfortable armchairs, it's the perfect place to relax with a drink and grab a bite to eat.

name: Scandic Opalen
abstract:
Our relaxed restaurant is the perfect choice for a bite to eat before or after a concert, trade fair, match or cinema visit. We serve a contemporary blend of international cuisine here; everything from herring and traditional slow-cooked dishes, to flavours from Asia and the US. Kids get their own menu and crayons and paper are provided as a fun gift, and can be put to very good use during a long dinner. There is also a playroom next to our restaurant for kids with energy to burn. 

Recharge your batteries in our relaxation area. Enjoy a calm moment in a hot sauna after a workout pass in our gym. We have 18 bright and spacious conference rooms to choose from for your meeting, party or event, with capacity for up to 700 people.

name: Scandic Örnsköldsvik
abstract: Ät en god måltid i vår moderna restaurang eller slå dig ned med en favoritdrink i baren. Träna i hotellets gym, simma några längder i den generösa inomhuspoolen eller finn lugn och avkoppling i relaxavdelningen med bastu. Hotellet erbjuder 9 mötesrum samt fri wifi överallt.

name: Scandic Ariadne
abstract: Visit our gym and afterwards you can relax in our sauna.

name: Scandic Sjöfartshotellet
abstract: Enjoy a delicious dinner in our hotel’s restaurant Sjofart, or sip your favorite drink in our bar. Weather permitting, food and beverage are also served on our roof terrace, with fantastic views of Saltsjon bay. We also have a well-equipped gym and relaxation suite with sauna.

name: Lannalodge
abstract: Alla boenden är förlagda på anläggningen med gångavstånd till de upplevelser som erbjuds. Med fokus på kvalitet och upplevelser i avslappande och sköna miljö.

name: Wallby säteri
abstract: Mitt i Smålands trädgård med utsikt över Skirösjön ligger Wallby Säteri, strax utanför Vetlanda. Med unika produkt som växlar efter årstiderna erbjuder säteriet en upplevelse där småländska smaker och natur står i fokus.

name: Camping Tiveden
abstract:
Sedan 2010 har vi byggt upp Camping Tiveden till en underbar plats att campa och bo på. Vi vill ge dig så många bekvämligheter som möjligt, samtidigt som du kan bara njuta av campinglivet och omgivningen. 
Mitt i den vilda naturen runt Tivedens nationalpark samt de charmiga små typiska svenska landsbygdsbyar.

name: Holiday Club Åre
abstract:
Man kan resa över hela världen i jakt på upplevelser. Men man kan också komma till Åre och Holiday Club - fjällens träningshotell. Packa med träningskläderna - med ett 800 kvm stort inglasat SATS-gym, motionsbassäng, spinningsal och yogasal med panoramautsikt över fjällvärlden - blir träningen en upplevelse.

Under vårt tak finns också lekfull familjeträning både utomhus och inomhus genom Active Inclusive. Dessutom väntar fler små och stora äventyr utanför dörren.

Hos oss bor du i rymliga hotellrum eller lägenheter mitt i Åre med fjället på den ena sidan av hotellet och Åresjön på den andra.

Vi har öppet hela året och ser fram emot att välkomna dig till oss! Entré till SATS med gruppträningsklasser och simning och bad ingår.

Nya Holiday Club Åre är en hyllning till naturen, det lokala och ett aktivt liv. Låt oss vara en hjälpande hand ut på fjället eller var med på de träningspass som körs varje dag hela året. Fråga oss om våra tips för dagen beroende på väder och vind och när du är hungrig är du välkommen till bords i vår nya restaurang Grow.

Vi vill att barnen ska trivas hos oss på Holiday Club Åre - för då vet vi att du som förälder trivs. Våra rum är rymliga och barnvänliga och när du bokar boende hos oss har du alltid fri entré till vårt bad och aktiviteterna i Active Inclusive. På hotellet finns massor att göra för barn - och fjället utanför är en lekstuga som aldrig tar slut!

Välkommen!

name: Blåsjöns fjällcamp
abstract:
Anläggningen är öppen från mars till augusti med vacker sjö utsikt.

Stugorna är fullt utrustade för självhushåll och båtar finns att hyra på plats.
Du som stuggäst med egen båt har kostnads fri båtplats brevid dom befintliga hyrbåtarna. Båtplatser bokas vid stugbokning.

Jakt
Egna jaktmarker och fiskevatten. Träningsmarker för har- och rävhundar samt stående fågelhundar.

Fiske
Båtuthyrning i Leipikvattnet, Ankarvattnet, Mesvattnet, Blåsjön och egna fiskevatten.

Övrigt
Vindskydd med grillplats vid sjön.

Hundhus med rastgårdar finns att låna.

Tillgänglighet.
Mars-Augusti

name: Pilgrimshotellet
abstract:
Anläggningens fokus är att erbjuda naturupplevelser i världsklass, men också att ge plats för reflektioner och tankar som inte alltid får plats i vardagen.

Från hotellet är det nära till vandringsturer och sevärdheter som fiske, skoterleder och Fjällparken vid Gäddede turistinformation.

Hotellet kan även erbjuda dig vandring och fiskeguider.

Inom en radie av ca 5 mil från Pilgrimshotellet hittar du sevärdheterna som du når med bil och i ett fall med båt. Men Gudfjelløya kan också ses från vägen.

Vildmarksvägen , Sveriges högsta asfalterade landsväg. Vägen passerar över Stekenjokk.
Korallgrottan, Sveriges längsta grotta. Besök sker med guide.
Bjurälven, erhållit pris som Geologiskt.
Hällingsåfallet, drygt 40 m högt vattenfall i Sveriges längsta kanjon
Gudfjelløya, ”Tunnsjöguden” är Europas högsta insjö Ö. Ett fjäll i sjön Tunnsjøen.
Avsätt en helg eller helst några extra dagar för upptäcka naturens under! 

Hotell och restaurang
I restaurang Pilgrim serveras lokalproducerade läckerheter med omtanke till miljö, natur och glada djur. Det är möjligt att köpa till en pilgrimsmatsäck för din utflykt. Hotellet drivs i alkoholfri inriktning. 

Hotellet har 60 bäddar i enkel- och dubbelrum och stugor.
Rummen är även tillgänglighetsanpassade och djurtillåtna.
Konferensrum upp till 25 personer samt bastu och bubbelpool finns vid sjökanten.
Vill du unna dig lite extra kan du hyra vår stuga med utomhusjacuzzi och bastu vid sjön. Ni har privat tillgång till jacuzzi och bastu under din vistelse.
Hotellet är öppet året runt och tre snabbladdare & fyra övernatt -ningsladdare finns. Laddningen ingår när du bor på hotellet.

name: Jormliens fjällgård
abstract:
Det finns 17 rum och alla rummen är olika med undantaget att det finns kallt och varmt vatten i alla. Toaletter finns i korridorerna, nyrenoverade duschar och bastu finns i källaren.

I matsalen serverars vilträtter som specialitet. Matsalen är stor och rymlig, och får plats med större sällskap upp till 75 personer.

Det finns ett sällskapsrum med ett litet bibliotek och ett tv-rum, för mys i soffan.

 Konferenser för mindre grupper, personalvård, kick off med mera. Med Fjällgården som utgångspunkt finns det fina möjligheter till vandring, exempelvis Raudekfjället med sin rika flora.

name: Hotell Åsgården
abstract:
Vårt mål är att du ska känna dig som hemma hos oss med personlig service och fräscha rum till ett bra pris. Förutom hemtrevlig miljö får du även nära till natursköna omgivningar som kan ge både inspiration och avkoppling.

Hotellet har tolv rum, varav fyra enkelrum. För småbarnsfamiljer har vi två rum att erbjuda med både dubbelsäng och en bäddsoffa. Alla rum har egen tv, wc, dusch och kylskåp. Under er vistelse här ingår frukost och gratis wifi. Ni har även tillgång till bastu och mikrovågsugn.

Vill du boka konferens?
Vi har även konferensrum med 20 sittplatser och går självklart att möblera om för att passa just era behov.
Hör av er till oss med önskemål kring er konferens så vi är
förberedda på vad ni behöver.

 Öppettider
Måndag-Fredag kl. 09.00-18.00
Lördag-Söndag kl. 10.00-18.00

name: Dentas Hotell
abstract:
Dentas hotell har en fin atmosfär för kurser, konferenser, affärsmöten och övernattningar.

 Hotellet har en omsorgsfull inredning och du kan välja att bo i läkarens, stinsens eller bilhandlarens rum. Den känsla hotellet vill förmedla är att du som gäst ska känna ”Här är du borta – fast känslan är att du är hemma”.

Rum: svit, enkelrum eller dubbelrum.

Spa med bubbelbad som har fem sittplatser.

Bastun, med ljus inredning, ligger intill, och har direkt anslutning till den stora altanen. Relaxavdelningen har mysig och tyst miljö att koppla av i.

 Lilla konferensen rymmer 15 personer.

name: HH&S – Högt, hett & säkert, Gåxsjö
abstract:
Hos oss kan du känna dig som hemma med personlig service, fräscha rum och lägenheter till ett bra pris. Förutom hemtrevlig miljö får du även fjällnära och natursköna omgivningar vid Gåxsjöns östra strand.

Hotellet har tre hotellrum och flera lägenheter med med både dubbelsäng och enkelsäng. Alla rum och lägenheter har eget kök, eller tillgång till kök. Alla våra boenden har fri snabb wifi, tv samt tillgång till tvättmaskin, vedeldad bastu och badtunna.

I vår restaurang går det bra att förboka frukost och middag om så önskas. Vår mysiga pub med fullständiga rättigheter ligger i anslutning till restaurangen.
Planera gärna din familjehögtid, eller kanske bröllop hos oss. Våra stora lokaler och direkta närhet till vackra Gåxsjö kyrka ger stora möjligheter. Vi tar också gärna emot cateringuppdrag.

Vill du boka konferens eller kontorsplats?
Vi har även flera konferensrum med 4 till 60 sittplatser samt tillgång till kontorsplatser.

Hör av dig till oss för en behovsanpassad lösning för dig.

name: Lia Ranch
abstract:
Camping
2014 utrustade vi vår camping med ett helt nytt servicehus med toaletter och dusch. Ny reception med lite försäljning samt större plats för husvagnar och husbilar samt helt nya elstolpar med mätare för säsongsuppställning. Det finns även en mysig grillkåta att krypa in i för att sitta under tak och grilla om det regnar.

Husvagnar och husbilar är välkomna från mitten av mars till och med november.

Tre stugor för uthyrning
Öringen och Rödingen är 28 kvadrat med fyra till fem bäddar i två sovrum, allrum, kök, dusch och toalett.

Timmerstugan är helt i timmer, med torvtak och färdigställdes för uthyrning 2018. Den har två enkelsängar samt bäddsoffa. Kök med spis, mikro och kylskåp. Toalett och dusch i servicehuset utanför. Vedkamin finns i stugan som sprider både värme och hög mysfaktor.

Fiske
Fisket i Ankarvattnet och älvarna runt om erbjuder ett fantastiskt fint fiske av enbart ädelfisken öring och röding. Vattensystemet har haft turen att klara sig ifrån regleringen, vilket leder till det fina fisket. Ankarvattnet ingår i Frostvikenkortet och Lia Ranch har försäljning av fiskekort och fiskeutrystning och båt- och kanouthyrning.

Guidade fjällrävsturer

name: Rossöns FVO
abstract:
Stugor
Härbret, Rossöns golfbana
Härbret ligger vid Rossöns golfbaneanläggning i Näsets by vid Näsån, 2 km från Rossön, och har nio bäddar. Häbret har i två separata rum med pentryn och ett loft med braskamin och tv.

I anslutning till härbret finns en vedeldad bastu och servicebyggnad med kök för självhushåll, toalett och dusch. I servicebyggnadens övervåning finns fem bäddar. I stughyran ingår sänglinne. Båt kan hyras under vistelsen.

Bodumstugan, Rossöns golfbana
Bodumstugan ligger vid Rossöns golfbaneanläggning i Näsets by vid Näsån, 2 km från Rossön. Stugan har kök för självhushåll, toalett, dusch och vedeldad bastu. I stugans övervåning finns två sovrum med 5 bäddar. I stughyran ingår sänglinne. Båt kan hyras under vistelsen.

Björken, Vallsjön
Stugan Björken ligger 15 km från Rossön. Den har två bäddar och är utrustad med gasolanläggning i form av kylskåp, spis och kamin. Extrabädd finns vid behov.

I anslutning till stugan finns 2-bäddars friggebod, utedass och båtbrygga. I stughyran ingår sänglinne. Båt kan hyras under vistelsen.

Om fisket
I Vallsjön finns stora utmaningar när det gäller sportfiske. Det är inte helt ovanligt att fyrakilosöringar utmanar. Effektivaste fisket har man från båt kring midsommartid när det större dagsländorna kläckts. Här finns båt och en stuga att hyra.

Trehörningen och Gröttjärn är nya spännande vatten som området förvaltar. I Trehörningen finns ett bestånd av självreproducerande röding. I Gröttjärn har ett spännande harrvatten skapats.

För den som vill ge sig ut på en lite längre fisketur är Byvattnet ett givet mål. Här och vid Harahällarna utmed Nagasjöåns mynning, kan man fiska öring i storslagen natur. En loftstuga finns för uthyrning vid Byvattnet.

Vattensystemet sammanfogas vid Bodumssjön som omgärdar Rossön med 18 mil stränder. Här finns många homar, vikar och näs som sommartid kan upplevas från turistbåten Bärgaren.

Dessutom kan vi erbjuda:
Försäljning av fiskekort
Uthyrning av båtar
Guidning
Weekendpaket
Småviltsjakt

name: Fjällsikten Tåsjöberget
abstract:
Restaurangen ligger på 635 meters höjd över havet och kan ta emot 150 sittande gäster. Boende erbjuder vi i form av tolv fyra-bädds stugor utrustade för självhushåll, totalt 48 bäddar.

Dessutom finns en rymlig konferens/nöjeslokal för större sammankomster.
Middagar, bröllop, minnesstunder, företagsevent, kickoff:er med mera genomförs året runt. Fantastisk utsikt och naturupplevelser.

Utsikten från restaurangen är bedårande, vid fint väder ser man 150 kilometer!
Fina möjligheter till vandring, fiske och allehanda naturupplevelser i området. Hundvänligt, både boendet och området

Kontakta oss gärna vid frågor eller bokningar av boende.

name: Blåsjöns fjällby
abstract:
Anläggningen har 48 bäddar fördelade på 6 stycken åtta-bäddsstugor.

Stugbyn är belägen på sydsluttningen av fjället Mesklumpen med utsikt över Stora Blåsjön och fjällen på andra sidan sjön.

Alla hus är rymliga, moderna och försedda med kök, WC/dusch, radio/TV.

8-bäddsstugorna har 4 sovrum, en extra toalett samt torkskåp.

Samtliga stugor ligger intill slalombacken som har 4 liftar och 12 nedfarter.

Fjällvandring direkt från dörren till botaniska, geologiska och kulturella utflyktsmål i närheten.

name: Basecamp Norråker
abstract:
Bo
Marjas stuga och Härbret - 
Marjas stuga är Norråkers äldsta hus, byggt i mitten av 1800-talet. Stugan är renoverad och moderniserad men har kvar sin ursprungliga charm. Marjas stuga ligger vid skogskanten i utkanten av byn, nära till allt men ändå isolerat. På gården finns också ett härbre med fler sängplatser.

Bomvaktarstugan- 
I denna härliga stuga bor du mindre än ett stenkast från sjön. Njut av lugnet och den fantastiska utsikten från köksbordet medan du väntar på att kokkaffet ska bli klart på vedspisen. Bomvaktarstugan har moderniserats med el men vattnet hämtar du från sjön. Som förr.

Parhuset 13A & 13B- 
På vägen ned mot sjön från Norråkers Handel ligger vårt parhus. Två lägenheter med separata kök och toaletter och plats för totalt sju personer.

Bo på lanthandel-
Lägenheten är fullt utrustad med kök, vardagsrum, tre sovrum med totalt fem sängar, dusch, wc och tv. Köket är fullt utrustat för självhushåll med spis med ugn, micro, kyl, frys, brödrost och kaffebryggare.

Norråkers Handel
Norråkers Handel är en charmig och lite annorlunda lanthandel. Här finns inte bara mjölk, ägg och bröd utan även ett imponerande utbud av goda ostar och andra delikatesser från när och fjärran, tyger från Sri Lanka, handgjorda knivar från byn och boende.

I butiken hittar du också en InfoPoint där du får information om närområdet kring Tåsjön. Ingen annanstans hittar du boenden som våra. Personligt, autentiskt och naturnära – men bekvämt!

Aktiviteter och äventyr
Det finns gott om upplevelser året om i vår omgivning. Hur vill du helst utforska och uppleva den magiska naturen omkring Norråker?

Skotertur med isfiske
Åka skidor med draghund
Häst och släde
Åk hundspann
Vandringar i skog och fjäll
Häst och vagn
Paddla kajak
Fiska
Hyra båt

name: Lofsdalen Home
abstract: Följ med till Lofsdalen Bear´s Den på björnspaning och se skogens största rovdjur i dess naturliga miljö. Har du tur får ni syn på älg, räv och järv också.

name: STF Sunne Hembygdsgård Bed and Breakfast
Tivedstorps Vandrarhem, Kafé och Kök
abstract:
Tivedstorp är en by med över 20 byggnader utplacerade över flera kullar –mitt i skogen! 
Byn är välbevarad med sina stugor med torvtak, gamla gärdesgårdar, ängar och hagar. 
Vandrarhem med 70 bäddar i rum och stugor. 
Kafé och Kök med rättigheter i vår Kaffestuga och Grillstuga. Återkommande kulturarrangemang med konst och musik. 
Vår egen Skogsträdgård, för framtidens hållbara matproduktion. Kapell, Badtunna, Bastu, Scen, Grillstuga, Festloge med mera. Bokningsbart för kurser, bröllop, konferenser och fester.

name: Björkbacken Karaktärshotell
abstract: Sommartid möter du lummiga grillområden, ett fräscht servicehus, en stor lekpark,  äventyrsgolf samt en vattenlekpark, Lovisas Pizzeria, Cajsas café med mat, fika och en liten servicebutik.

name: Vox Hotell
abstract: Vox Hotel ligger mitt i city och placerar sig tydligt på kartan som ett förstklassigt livsstilshotell, med fokus på design och bekvämlighet för den moderna resenären.

name: Njut av Natur & Komfort under alla årstider
Toftaholm Herrgård
abstract: Toftaholm ligger nära från E4:an söder om Värnamo. Passa på att välja gamla riksvägen - Riksettan i stället när du kör vidare. Lugnare takt, nära naturen och mycket att se. Redig, småländsk ostkaka serveras sommartid på närbelägna Sussies Café.

name: Åkerby Herrgård - AuroraHut
abstract:
•	Unik logiupplevelse i Nora Bergslag: AuroraHut erbjuder en boendeupplevelse som är mitt i naturen, perfekt för dig som vill kombinera äventyr med avkoppling.
•	Miljövänlig logi i naturdestinationer: Turismens nya gröna trend – upplev AuroraHut, som kombinerar modern design med en hållbar och naturnära livsstil.
•	Hotellklass i naturen: Trots det naturnära läget får du bekvämligheten av ett boende med hotellstandard, mitt i de vackra landskapen.
•	AuroraHut – Igloobåten som är fri från marken och vardagen: Detta flytande boende kan användas året om och erbjuder ett annorlunda sätt att uppleva naturen.
•	Bekvämt boende för två personer: AuroraHut är utrustad för en lyxig och upplevelserik vistelse med allt du behöver, inklusive en dubbelsäng, kök, nedfällbart matbord, matkällare och toalett.
•	360-graders utsikt från golv till tak: Njut av panoramavyer över naturen och stjärnhimlen från ditt eget rum, med en design som öppnar upp hela rummet mot omgivningen.
•	Specialfunktion för vinterfiske: Ett pilkhål i golvet gör det möjligt att pilka inomhus, bekvämt och varmt även när vinterkylan biter utanför.
•	Smarta bekvämligheter: Ett varmt torkskåp håller ytterkläderna torra, och det finns förvaringsutrymme för bagage under sängen.
•	Anpassad komfort: Justera värme och belysning efter eget tycke, och dra för gardinerna för extra insynsskydd när du vill ha lite extra privatliv.
•	Alltid uppkopplad: AuroraHut erbjuder wifi, så du kan hålla kontakten även när du befinner dig mitt i naturens stillhet.

name: Hyr stuga på landet

name: Bo i genuin gårdsmiljö

name: Vandrarhem mitt i naturen
abstract: På Fallängetorp kan alla uppleva en ekologisk och KRAV-certifierad lantgård med kor, får, grisar, hästar, hundar, katter och höns. Om du har nedsatt rörelseförmåga, prova gärna att ta dig runt på gården med det terränggående fordonet Zoom Uphill, zoomen, eller varför inte en tur med traktor och vagn?

name: Fredagsmys i centrala Västerås
abstract: Detta paket lämpar sig lika bra till paret, kompisarna som till familjen. Se till att avsluta arbetsveckan och inleda helgen på bästa vis. När du bokar detta så väntar en ”Fredagsmys-låda” med snacks, mousserande vin, läsk och godis samt badrock och tofflor på rummet. Vill du att det ska vara fredag någon annan dag i veckan så går det alldeles utmärkt att boka detta paket en annan valfri dag. Låt fredagsmyset bli en ännu lyxigare stund på veckan.

name: Wärdshuset Dickens'
abstract: När ni bokar rum hos oss behöver vi veta er ungefärliga ankomsttid eftersom vi inte har bemannat dygnet runt. Vi behöver också veta i förväg om ni har med er hund, samt era eventuella särskilda kostbehov.

name: Vintermys på landet
abstract: Rosenberg ligger på länsgränsen mellan Uppland och Västmanland i närheten av riksväg 70, ca 1 h från Stockholm. Ett perfekt övernattningsställe på väg upp mot Dalarna och fjällen.

name: Borgjaur Jakt- och fiskecamp

name: Garpens Fyrplats

name: Ödevata Gårdshotell
abstract: Gården mellan sjöarna ligger 10 km utanför Emmaboda, och bara en bilfärd ifrån Glasriket, Öland och Astrid Lindgrens Vimmerby. Gården har utvecklats från en nerlagd statlig kriminalvårdsanstalt till en fiske- och aktivitetsgård med tillgång till härlig natur och med flera boenden som håller mycket hög kvalité. Ödevata är en fullbordad turistanläggning i klassiskt bemärkelse, men samtidigt är det hem och hjärtefråga för värdfamiljen som bor där.

name: Kylås Vildmarksby
abstract: Här kan du även fiska, bada, vandra runt sjön, ro båt eller paddla kanot. Detta är en plats att umgås med familj och vänner och vara offline en stund.
